r-text, .mbr-section-btn\"><b>арт:</b> 07<br><b>ремень для штанов</b><br><b>цена:</b> 12800 тг<br></p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-2\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"index.html#form6-e\" class=\"btn btn-primary item-btn\" target=\"_blank\" data-app-placeholder=\"Введите Текст\">Заказать</a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{cardsWidth}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"item-img\">\n                        <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/d09ad180d0b5d0b0d182d0b8d0b220d0b1d0b5d0b720d0bdd0b0d0b7d0b2d0b0d0bdd0b8d18f2067-596x596.png\" alt=\"Кожаный ремень KARYA\" data-slide-to=\"7\" data-bs-slide-to=\"7\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"item-content\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n                        <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Кожаный ремень KARYA</b></h5>\n                        <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-1\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">\n                            <i>Card Subtitle</i>\n                        </h6>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\"><b>арт:</b> 08<br><b>ремень для штанов</b><br><b>цена:</b> 12800 тг<br></p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-2\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"index.html#form6-e\" class=\"btn btn-primary item-btn\" target=\"_