          "_name": "features1",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features25\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Icons\" name=\"showIcon\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" name=\"iconColor\" value=\"#000000\" selected condition=\"showIcon\">\n        <select title=\"Columns\" name=\"columns\">\n            <option value=\"3\" selected>4</option>\n            <option value=\"4\">3</option>\n            <option value=\"6\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"12\">1</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background4.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#a55959\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row mb-5\">\n            <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>Почему выбирают нас</b></h3>\n                <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n                    List main features of your project in this block\n                </h5>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-center\">\n                    <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-cash mobi-mbri\"></span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><p><b>Премиальное качество</b></p></h5>\n                    <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Мы отбираем только качественные материалы и проверенные бренды, чтобы каждая вещь служила долго.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-center\">\n                    <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbrib-magic-stick\"></span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Стиль и актуальность</b></h5>\n                    <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">В нашем каталоге — современные модели, которые подчеркивают статус и индивидуальность.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-center\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbri-briefcase\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Универсальный выбор</b></h5>\n                        <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Одежда и аксессуары подходят как для повседневной жизни, так и для делового стиля.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
