          "_name": "testimonials2",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"testimonials2\" group=\"Testimonials\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" plugins=\"mobirise-icons2\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"fullWidth\" title=\"Full Width\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Name\" name=\"showName\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Position\" name=\"showPosition\">\n        <select title=\"Columns\" name=\"columns\">\n            <option value=\"3\" selected>4</option>\n            <option value=\"4\">3</option>\n            <option value=\"6\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"12\">1</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#a55959\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    \n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>Отзывы наших клиентов<br><br></b></h3>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}} active\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">Купил здесь сорочки и брюки — приятно удивило качество. Ткань плотная, сидит отлично, после стирки форма не теряется. Теперь беру здесь и галстуки, и ремни, потому что всё выглядит аккуратно и носить удобно.</p>\n                    <div class=\"d-flex mb-md-0 mb-4\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/d0bad0b0d0b7d0b0d185-100x133.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"1\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                            <p class=\"name mbr-fonts-style mb-1\" mbr-if=\"showName\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".name\"><b>Султан А.</b></p>\n                            <p class=\"position mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showPosition\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".position\"><br></p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">Заказывал сумку и портмане. Качество реально хорошее, кожа плотная, выглядит дорого.</p>\n                    <div class=\"d-flex mb-md-0 mb-4\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/d0bed189d188d183d0bad0bed184d0b0d189d188d184-100x133.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"2\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                            <p class=\"name mbr-fonts-style mb-1\" mbr-if=\"showName\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".name\"><b>Мадина Булатова</b></p>\n                            <p class=\"position mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showPosition\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".position\"><br></p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">Был день рождения у подруги , подарила ключницу бренда KARYA - подруге понравилась, кожа наттуральная, цены не дорогие.</p>\n                    <div class=\"d-flex mb-md-0 mb-4\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/d180d188d0b3d183d188d0b3d0b0d180d183d186d0b3d188d184d0b0d180d184d0b3d188-100x133.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"3\" data-bs-slide-to=\"3\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                            <p class=\"name mbr-fonts-style mb-1\" mbr-if=\"showName\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".name\"><b>Екатерина Васильева</b></p>\n                            <p class=\"position mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showPosition\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".position\"><br></p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">Заказывал несколько позиций: сорочки, брюки и ключницы. Всё пришло аккуратно, вещи хорошо сочетаются между собой. Теперь не нужно искать по разным магазинам.</p>\n                    <div class=\"d-flex mb-md-0 mb-4\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/d0bcd180d0bfd0bcd180d0bcd180d0bc-100x133.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                            <p class=\"name mbr-fonts-style mb-1\" mbr-if=\"showName\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".name\"><b>Иван Прохоров</b></p>\n                            <p class=\"position mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showPosition\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".position\"><br></p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vhAnbuc9qN",
          "_anchor": "testimonials2-1b",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            ".mbr-overlay": {
              "background-color": "@overlayColor",
              "opacity": "@overlayOpacity"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "form": {
              "@media (min-width: 992px)": {
                "width": "50%"
              },
              ".mbr-section-btn": {
                "text-align": "center",
                "width": "100%",
                ".btn": {
                  "width": "100%"
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#000000"
            }
          },
          "_name": "form6",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"form6\" group=\"Forms\" plugins=\"formstyler, datepicker\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\">\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffeada\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.4\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"usedRecaptcha\" value=\"false\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"(overlay && bg.type=='image')\"></div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-head\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n            <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n                <b>Контакты</b></h3>\n            <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n                Contacts Subtitle\n            </h4>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center mt-4\">\n            <div mbr-form class=\"col-lg-8 mx-auto mbr-form\">\n                <form action=\"alexandrakh2008@gmail.com\" name=\"Form Name\" method=\"POST\" data-rcpha_sitekey=\"\" data-rcpha_secretkey=\"\" class=\"mbr-form form-with-styler mx-auto\" data-verified=\"alexandrakh2008@gmail.com\">\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert class=\"alert alert-success col-12\">Скоро ответим на Ваш запрос!!</div>\n                        <div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert-danger class=\"alert alert-danger col-12\">\n                            Oops...! some problem!\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"dragArea row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group mb-3\" data-for=\"name\">\n                            <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"имя\" data-form-field=\"name\" class=\"form-control\" value>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group mb-3\" data-for=\"email\">\n                            <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"почта\" data-form-field=\"email\" class=\"form-control\" value>\n                        </div>\n                        <div data-for=\"phone\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group mb-3\">\n                            <input type=\"tel\" name=\"phone\" placeholder=\"телефон\" data-form-field=\"phone\" class=\"form-control\" value>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto mbr-section-btn align-center\" mbr-buttons=\"true\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-mbrBtnAdd\"><a type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Введите Текст\"><span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-share mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>Отправить</a></div>\n                    </div>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_anchor": "form6-1g",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "vhApkl885L",
